https://fullfact.org/health/leicester-co.description: It is still too early to give a definitive explanation for why Leicester’s outbreak happened.

https://fullfact.org/online/argos-iphone.title: Argos £2 iPhone promotion is not genuine - Full Fact
https://fullfact.org/online/argos-iphone.description: Yet another fake Argos offer is being shared on Facebook.

https://fullfact.org/online/coronavirus-.title: Covid-19 is not ‘a lie’ - Full Fact

https://fullfact.org/online/wuhan-virus-.description: Coronavirus is not one single virus: it’s a family of them.

https://fullfact.org/immigration/refugee.title: Do refugees have to stay in the first safe country they reach? - Full Fact

https://fullfact.org/europe/350-million-.title: £350 million EU claim "a clear misuse of official statistics" - Full Fact
https://fullfact.org/europe/350-million-.description: After we leave the EU, we cannot take back control of £350 million a week.

https://fullfact.org/online/king-charles.description: The original video shows the King revealing his official portrait, not a poster of Benjamin Netanyahu.

https://fullfact.org/online/people-did-d.title: People did die of Covid-19 in Ireland in August - Full Fact

https://fullfact.org/health/puppies-cani.description: The BBC’s live blog confused Covid-19 with canine coronavirus

https://fullfact.org/online/ballot-paper.title: Any party can apply for a ‘slogan’ to be included on a ballot paper - Full Fact

https://fullfact.org/health/cunningham-j.title: Alex Cunningham and Boris Johnson  both used the wrong figures about health inequality - Full Fact
https://fullfact.org/health/cunningham-j.description: Most men in Stockton live much longer than men in Ethiopia, but one ward is far worse off, and the gap in UK life expectancy is widening.

https://fullfact.org/online/telegraph-fa.title: The Telegraph has not published an article about ‘emergency detainment camps’ in the Falklands - Full Fact
https://fullfact.org/online/telegraph-fa.description: The newspaper confirmed that it has never published any such article.

https://fullfact.org/health/covid-vaccin.title: The Covid-19 vaccines have not only been tested on healthy people as claimed - Full Fact
https://fullfact.org/health/covid-vaccin.description: A video on Facebook makes various claims about Covid-19 vaccines which are wrong or could use more context.

https://fullfact.org/health/boots-latera.title: Boots isn’t selling lateral flow tests ‘the taxpayer has already paid for’ - Full Fact
https://fullfact.org/health/boots-latera.description: It’s been falsely claimed on social media that the retailer has been ‘given’ taxpayer funded Covid-19 tests to sell back to the public.

https://fullfact.org/online/crashed-figh.title: Meme does not show crashed Ukrainian F-16 fighter jet - Full Fact
https://fullfact.org/online/crashed-figh.description: The image in the meme is of a US Air Force plane that crashed in California in 2019 due to a mechanical malfunction.

https://fullfact.org/immigration/about-3.title: About 3.2 million citizens of other EU countries live in the UK - Full Fact
https://fullfact.org/immigration/about-3.description: It’s likely that around half arrived between 2006 and 2014.

https://fullfact.org/economy/boris-johns.description: While comparing economic growth to carbon emissions, Mr Johnson claimed the economy has grown 73% under this government. It has grown by around 20%.

https://fullfact.org/online/severance-pa.title: A Cabinet minister was not entitled to £470,000 severance pay after two days on the job - Full Fact

https://fullfact.org/online/center-parcs.description: The promotions are not linked to Center Parcs.

https://fullfact.org/online/michelle-oba.description: The false claim is another example of baseless theories circulating about Mrs Obama’s gender.

https://fullfact.org/online/christian-er.description: Users on social media are sharing false claims that the Danish footballer had been vaccinated days before becoming ill on the pitch.

https://fullfact.org/news/false-2017-vid.title: Video shows Iraqi MP describing actions of Islamic State, not Hamas - Full Fact

https://fullfact.org/online/video-bazaar.title: Market video shows scenes in Pakistan, not Bradford - Full Fact

https://fullfact.org/europe/ask-full-fac.title: Ask Full Fact: Europol and diplomatic immunity - Full Fact

https://fullfact.org/online/argos-playst.title: Argos is not selling PlayStation 5 consoles for £3 - Full Fact

https://fullfact.org/online/iceland-ceo-.title: Iceland’s CEO is not offering free food to people who like a Facebook page - Full Fact

https://fullfact.org/online/maria-elena-.title: An Italian politician did not expose her underwear during her swearing-in ceremony - Full Fact
